        [
          "Gangrel who fits in both inside and outside the Camarilla, has used this skill for intellegence and reconn for the Camarilla in its Sabbat Wars.",
          "",
          "",
          "",
          "",
          "",
          "",
          "",
          "Jenn Wolfe"
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You had a foot in two worlds. Your father came to America from Scotland and created a life for himself in the back country of North Carolina. He fell in love with your mother, a Cherokee woman, with whom he settled and raised a family. You had a foot in two worlds, your mother's and your father's, and you found yourself splitting between both seemelessly. Your value going between communities drew the attention of your sire, a Gangrel who watched you for some time before Embracing you. The Camarilla was, in their mind, a necessary evil, a sect of vampires that had its faults but provided protection for the Gangrel. Being able to walk in two worlds was effective for reconnaissance work, and you became a valuable asset along the East Coast in Camarilla strong holds, particularly in dealing with Anarchs and unaffiliated vampires. You played a key role in the East Coast Wars against the Sabbat, and now that those wars are over your skills are being sought elsewhere. Los Angeles was part of the Anarch Free State, now it is in Camarilla territory and is threatened by the Sabbat. Your skills are of use here in determining the best course of action for the prince"
        ],
